'''Sean Bellerby''' is an Australian entrepreneur. He is the founding CEO and President of [[GoSnow, Inc.]], a Los Angeles-based investor backed software company known for taking the worldwide snow sports industry on demand.

Bellerby graduated from [[Macquarie University]] in 2012 with an [[MBA]], and Master of Marketing degree.<ref>[http://www.gosnow.in/about Sean Bellerby bio] at [[GoSnow]]</ref>{{Primary source inline|date=March 2017}} In addition to [[Macquarie University]], and prior to starting GoSnow, Bellerby had spent 12 years in senior business development roles in [[U.S]] enterprise software companies such as [[Mercury Interactive]], [[Intel Security]], and [[CA Technologies]] in varying locations around the world. His last tenure in the enterprise software business was at [[CA Technologies]] as an executive responsible for taking new cloud services to market through global service provider partnerships.

Bellerby co-founded GoSnow in 2016 with American Scott Anfang. Its first product was a meet-up app for skiers and snowboarders which was credited as a world first.<ref name="GrindTV">{{cite web|url= 
http://www.grindtv.com/snowboarding/new-app-like-tinder-for-g-rated-mountain-hookups/#JeXHjS5MR7HJAEaD.97|title= New app like Tinder for G-rated mountain hookups |first= Julie |last= Kailus |date= March 15, 2016 |work= [[GrindTV.com|GrindTV]]}}</ref><ref name="The Denver Post">{{cite web|url= 
http://www.denverpost.com/2016/02/14/gosnow-mobile-app-connects-strangers-friends-on-slopes/ |title= GoSnow mobile app connects strangers, friends on slopes |first= Erica |last= Robbie |date= February 7, 2016 |work= [[The Denver Post]]}}</ref>

In January 2017, GoSnow innovatively took the snows sports industry on demand by releasing its on demand bookings platform for snow sports instructors and activities around the world.<ref name="SnowsBest">{{cite web|url= 
http://www.snowsbest.com/gosnow-launches-on-demand-booking-platform-for-ski-instructors/|title= GoSnow launches on demand bookings platform for ski instructors |first= Rachael |last= Oakes Ash |date= January 31, 2017 |work= [[SnowsBest.com|SnowsBest]]}}</ref> <ref name="WeAreLATech">{{cite web|url= 
http://podcast.wearelatech.com/episodes/69224-gosnow-world-s-first-on-demand-approach-to-booking-snow-sports-la-startup-spotlight-sean-bellerby/|title= GoSnow World’s First On-Demand Approach To Booking Snow Sports: LA Startup Spotlight – Sean Bellerby |first= Espree |last= Devora |date= May 10, 2017 |work= [[WeAreLATech.com|WeAreLATech]]}}</ref>

